| 4. Thoroughness in Problem   | Does the student address all aspects of the problem? |                       |
|    Solving                    | Are all necessary steps included in the solution?    |                       |
|-------------------------------|------------------------------------------------------|-----------------------|
| 5. Understanding of Concepts | Does the student grasp mathematical concepts well?    |                       |
|                               | Can the student apply these concepts effectively?    |                       |
|-------------------------------|------------------------------------------------------|-----------------------|
| 6. Adherence to Instructions | Did the student follow all given instructions?       |                       |
|                               | Is the work completed according to the required     |                       |
|                               | format or method?                                    |                       |
